<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta__inner container container--padded">
    <div class="cta__content">
      <h2 class="cta__heading">
        <span class="cta__heading-cap">La</span> tua vista non aspetta. Prenota oggi il tuo esame gratuito.
      </h2>
      <p class="cta__body">
        L'esame della vista è gratuito, senza prenotazione obbligatoria e senza impegno — vieni a
        trovarci quando vuoi.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="https://wa.me/393386570987" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta__btn">Prenota la tua visita</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-dark);
    min-height: 32.1875em; /* 515px */
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5em;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding-block: 3.75em;
  }

  .cta__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25em;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.167;
    color: var(--color-text-white);
    letter-spacing: -1.44px;
    max-width: 17.375em; /* 834px / 48px */
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  .cta__heading-cap {
    text-transform: capitalize;
  }

  .cta__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-white-soft);
    max-width: 41.5em; /* 664px */
  }

  .cta__btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.75em 1.25em;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-text-white);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ===================== Responsive ===================== */
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .cta__heading {
      font-size: 2.5em;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .cta {
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .cta__inner {
      padding-block: 2.5em;
      gap: 2em;
    }

    .cta__heading {
      font-size: 1.75em;
    }

    .cta__btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
